<ul>
<li><i>The Greek Way</i>, Edith Hamilton, W. W. Norton &amp; Co., NY, 1993.</li>
<li><i>Sailing the Wine-Dark Sea, Why the Greeks Matter</i>, Thomas Cahill, Nan A. Talese an imprint of Doubleday, NY, 2003.</li>
</ul>


